  <h2 class="section-title">Register what you need.<br>Override what you want.</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">Every feature beyond core bars is an extension. Free extensions ship with the package. Paid bundles add structure, flare, and analysis.</p>
  <div class="ext-grid">
    <div class="ext-card">
      <div class="ext-card-header">
        <h3>Today Marker</h3>
        <span class="ext-badge free">Free</span>
