      <div class="ext-card-header">
        <h3>Phase Grouping</h3>
        <span class="ext-badge paid">Organize</span>
      </div>
      <p>Collapsible phase rows that span their children. Color-coded thin bars. Click to expand or collapse entire phases.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ext-card">
      <div class="ext-card-header">
        <h3>Milestones</h3>
        <span class="ext-badge paid">Organize</span>
      </div>
      <p>Diamond markers for deadlines and checkpoints. Phase-colored borders, progress fill bottom-to-top, glass highlight.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

